Title: Availability of host group should be reachable via host groups view
Component: multisite
State: open
Date: 2015-02-09 12:23:08
Targetversion: 1.2.7
Class: todo

Currently you have to use the Host search. The reason is that the datasource hostgroups
and appearantly hostsbygroup do not support availability. This should be fixed so that
availability is always possible.
